{
  "stem": "22803.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so that was just part of-- of the lessons we learned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the same continued later on in high school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, the Jewish community was much-- you know, was small.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really-- I-- you know, I guess they were not concentrated in-- certainly not where I lived in one area, so there were Jewish and non-Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think in the early years, we probably inter-mixed quite freely.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I think of it, I guess the children that I visited with or saw were probably mostly Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did have-- now I'm thinking I did have non-Jewish friends that came to the house [BACKGROUND NOISE] too, you know, to play.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the children that when we played, you know, street games or so, they were mostly non-Jewish, the neighbors' children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- well, we went to the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to the main synagogue in Munich, which was in the city, and mainly only on the religious-- on the high holidays.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Later on when my father didn't work anymore towards the end, he used to go Saturday morning services.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe that my father probably came from a more religious background than my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know, we didn't keep a kosher home or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I had very-- I mean, we had very good religious instruction, because we had very good teachers, apart-- you know, the history and the learning Hebrew, apart from keeping the-- you know, the Orthodox rules, which we didn't do.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I think I was never a good student.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very immature, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was small in stature.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was always-- we were always lined up according to height.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
